{"tid":1872481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【回帶】無綫《東張西望》撐政府 狂踩港視未達標","createTime":"2020-02-10T06:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T07:36:17.000Z","uid":2054,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d621642a63d528962114ba7b05aa0c1dd287ec68","tid":1872481,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:06:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20131105/51875563\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20131105%2F51875563&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVf3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=069e9911\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20131105%2F51875563&h=be18839a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20131105/51875563</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20131105/large/1383653699_7317.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20131105%2Flarge%2F1383653699_7317.jpg&h=333d60d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被指為免費電視既得利益者之一的無綫電視，今晚利用時事娛樂節目《東張西望》整個時段，炮製半小時特備節目，力撐政府增發兩個牌照是顧及公眾利益，又稱建立電視台「好複雜」，免費電視廣告收入極不穩定，政府要持平衡發牌影響。<br />\n<br />\n節目一開始就諷刺港視將製作好的劇集放上Youtube播放，指建立電視台與「單純將上網分享係差天共地兩回事。」主持又朗讀政府發牌的11項因素，羅列出3個申請者在財政、技術和頻道數目等情況，又稱一個電視台一年約要有4,000小時節目播放，但港視只完成1170小時，力踩港視製作未達標。節目又引用一些收費電視資料，分析免費電視市場。<br />\n<br />\n近半小時的節目，不斷引述官員及行政會議成員過去3星期撐發2個牌照的言論、相關法則等，亦只引述一名市場學系教授分析指免費電視是公營機構，要負上社會負任，但並無分析港視不獲發牌的原因和市民意見。節目又指港視未有講明將提供多少條英語頻道，但事實上港視已表明將有1條英語頻道、1條綜合中文頻道及28條其他頻道。<br />\n<br />\n節目尾聲更批評有人在網上煽動市民發起罷看電視，更令「與世無爭、為市民帶來歡樂」的節目主持人受到人身攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日港視正式超越無綫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSUv4h0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSUv4h0.jpg&h=b9cf2da1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0ac6f0cfc09ed1059f1106b7b8b509f3ef6e9fa","tid":1872481,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:08:26.000Z","msg":"咩app"},{"pid":"9e7f43ee1c0d7a79a54130909011f2764d781288","tid":1872481,"uid":204539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:10:00.000Z","msg":"好耐無見何傲芝個含撚嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4effe035cdc65d2024d55487ee7791fc96fdaaf6","tid":1872481,"uid":53003,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KpggjDi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpggjDi.jpg&h=4ef17f5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e22ca122884767d7c052f6dd3df1964fed501ce8","tid":1872481,"uid":31962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4effe035cdc65d2024d55487ee7791fc96fdaaf6","tid":1872481,"uid":53003,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KpggjDi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpggjDi.jpg&h=4ef17f5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n20年後再冇TVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092041790bd790e24ba7457514278e978f87a503","tid":1872481,"uid":276525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:12:24.000Z","msg":"所以689當時真係用心良苦啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104758b9819fcdcdd62f3d8a46507d694c572a25","tid":1872481,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T06:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d3b34b14971d5bfb3603ef10500361fe985e75","tid":1872481,"uid":83328,